<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-the-name-of">in the name of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-in-sbs-sths-name">1.<strong>在…名下；以…的名义；代表 (in sb’s / sth’s name)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve booked a table in your name. 
我已经用你的名字预订了一张桌子。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I arrest you in the name of the law. 
我依法逮捕你。</p></div></div>